**Path 2 — preserveservice SLO violation:**
```
ts-consign-service (120 SEVERE NonUniqueResultException, HIGH_CPU 2.29 cores, max latency 2.95s)
  → ts-preserve-service (HIGH_ERROR_RATE: "Order already exist") ← SLO violation
  → ts-ui-dashboard (HTTP 500 errors on consign lookup)
```
